msg":"趙雲同真田幸村啊？<br />\n你當全港都偽進仔智商？"},{"pid":"74b50a6b69480adb4308a4fe639f4fe19db7d016","tid":1350311,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"兩個咋？dllm"},{"pid":"b5df3191d59aafd7f57efc8f5f091c69c46b7a02","tid":1350311,"uid":133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"兩個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌啲毅進仔真係弱智"},{"pid":"8ad24635e370e3a62e71351b0d71aaed84b2e91c","tid":1350311,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e78a4f3b9f17afff84729d3f50e9fc669768f90","tid":1350311,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2x7DQUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2x7DQUV.png&h=791635de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好清楚我地武力升級有限，啲狗仲有好多武器未出，包括實彈同水炮車，呢啲傷害力好高，足以打散我地陣勢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">硬撼對我地係絕對不利</span><br />\n<br />\n遍地開花是有用的，最緊要係打<span style=\"color: red;\">消耗戰</span><br />\n<br />\n警察只有3萬個，佢地冇可能短時間補充到（除非佢地搵國安扮警察，但係數量唔會多，因為好難落命令同埋組織戰術）<br />\n<br />\n而家夏天佢地下下都出曬防暴裝，朝早企到夜，對佢地身心都造成好大負荷，相反我地可以休息，可以補給，人數多到可以輪住做<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要拎住個<span style=\"color: red;\">主導權</span><br />\n<br />\n1. Be water，唔好戀戰<br />\n<br />\n呢個講咗好耐，但而家唔係講緊執生咁簡單，而係要變成主動一方，撚狗式遊走。<br />\n<br />\n我地逼佢地動員，但唔好引佢地升級武力。喺清場之前我地可以好似以前咁挑釁。<span style=\"color: red;\">當我地逼到佢地要清場嘅時候，我地就要毫不猶豫即刻散</span>，唔好戀戰。<span style=\"color: red;\">可以轉換場地，等佢地重新佈防，又或者留力去第二日</span><br />\n<br />\n總之我地<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好畀時間佢地休息</span>，雖然我地都會有體力消耗，但同佢地比我地會消耗得慢好多<br />\n<br />\n如果啲狗好似七一咁突然走曬去休息呢？我地就唔好畀機會佢地休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻升級，逼曬佢地翻出嚟之後又走，令佢地keep住精神繃緊<br />\n<br />\n2. 單一焦點，唔好浪費彈藥<br />\n<br />\n每一次行動都應該事先傾好，制定一個明確嘅目標。<span style=\"color: red;\">當是日目標達成之後，唔好即日觸發第二個事件</span>！好似琴日咁，噴黑國徽同臨時立法會宣言相衝，喺港島嘅焦點就去曬國徽度，我地又浪費咗一粒彈藥。"},{"pid":"c37bc7ab5ff81fb2ed34a2b21c2f3e165303c8ac","tid":1350311,"uid":274712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"黑警幾時死呀？快能啲死曬佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da72aae7aa4976702673b9d916f34bc881ae4e17","tid":1350311,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1d9a245ecb6e014b0e9184fdfc4dab585c19f8","tid":1350311,"uid":19698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"2個人就集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7278a9676003d183311825083fa301289d6153ff","tid":1350311,"uid":261753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"比多d安家費，交多 d人啦，又唔係無錢"},{"pid":"8fbadc6319d1c30beeaff55f131823478b042f93","tid":1350311,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:48:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你唔係想咁樣就當交代啊下"},{"pid":"e71dd56dffe644b2a50bebc7406e9343e872afde","tid":1350311,"uid":114193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:48:42.000Z","msg":"中流彈既就暴動罪<br />\n真落手打大肚婆既就非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6731e49a602b3f9252d95deb94c217f42c91489e","tid":1350311,"uid":76558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"百鳩幾人拎晒鐵通滕條 打到落車廂 撕殺列車 告非法集結<br />\n<br />\n和平示威 又要食催淚彈 橡膠彈 布彈 就告暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p